snippet: After watching the United States go winless in four straight games for the first time since he took over as coach three years ago, Jurgen Klinsmann had a harsh assessment of the Americans' post-World Cup performances....

headline.print_headline: Klinsmann Says US Failed 'to Digest' World Cup
headline.main: Klinsmann Says US Failed 'to Digest' World Cup

lead_paragraph: After watching the United States go winless in four straight games for the first time since he took over as coach three years ago, Jurgen Klinsmann had a harsh assessment of the Americans' post-World Cup performances.
